00:19:48.720 --> 00:19:49.950
So pretty straightforward.

00:19:49.950 --> 00:19:52.580
But I hope you've
seen and you've

00:19:52.580 --> 00:19:55.200
enjoyed there's a very
intuitive picture.

00:19:55.200 --> 00:19:57.250
But the correlation
function-- if you just

00:19:57.250 --> 00:19:59.350
look at it from the
perspective of the atoms,

00:19:59.350 --> 00:20:01.870
how do I experience
a coherent field?

00:20:01.870 --> 00:20:03.970
You put in simply
the diffusive motion.

00:20:03.970 --> 00:20:08.620
You can exactly calculate
what the line shape is.

00:20:08.620 --> 00:20:11.420
And that's definitely
something you would not

00:20:11.420 --> 00:20:14.750
have known how to do it
without this formalism.

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:15.250
OK.

00:20:23.520 --> 00:20:25.060
I have a question for you.

00:20:25.060 --> 00:20:34.110
And this is, how does the
spectrum for diffusive motion

00:20:34.110 --> 00:20:35.860
