01:12:40.270 --> 01:12:42.520
has two frequencies.

01:12:42.520 --> 01:12:44.940
So therefore, our
perturbation Hamiltonian

01:12:44.940 --> 01:12:48.100
is what we had so far
for monochromatic field.

01:12:48.100 --> 01:12:50.450
But then we have
an additional term

01:12:50.450 --> 01:12:53.630
where we just change the
