01:13:20.870 --> 01:13:25.720
And again, we have two
such possibilities--

01:13:25.720 --> 01:13:28.410
one at omega 1,
one at omega 2, one

01:13:28.410 --> 01:13:32.175
driven by field 1, the
other one driven by field 2.

01:13:36.140 --> 01:13:41.530
And yeah, we all have
the counter-rotating and

01:13:41.530 --> 01:13:42.280
