01:16:08.650 --> 01:16:10.790
me just finish the argument.

01:16:10.790 --> 01:16:13.280
So we have now an expression
in second-order perturbation

01:16:13.280 --> 01:16:14.260
theory.

01:16:14.260 --> 01:16:17.150
What is the amplitude
